	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S[alutem] d[ico].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Comitia <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustana</placeName> aiunt esse dissoluta.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accepi narrationem imperat[ori] 19. maii oblatam ab omnibus imperii ordinibus de eo institutum, an agnoscant <persName type="auto_name">Palatinum Augustanae</persName> confessionis socium.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In causa iustificationis et summa salutis agnoscunt socium, in causa coenae dominicae <persName type="auto_name">Zvinglianum</persName> esse aiunt; se tamen periculum facturos, an ante discessum cum eo possint transigere.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Alioqui<note xml:id="fn1" type="footnote" n="1">oder: Alioquin?.</note> enim nolle et ab imperatore non postulare, ut vel <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName> vel alii cum eo consentientes excludantur pace religionis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Neque hac re velle occasionem dare exteris persequendi eos, qui aliter quam ipsi sentiant de coena.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ipsos vero omnino constituisse in professione confessionis <placeName ref="l1976" cert="high">Augustanae</placeName> constanter perseverare.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Putant autem <placeName ref="l749" cert="high">Saxonem</placeName> vel <persName type="auto_name">Hessum</persName> huius moderationis authores vel saltem adiutores fuisse.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si perrexerit <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName>, de quo nihil dubitamus, fractae sunt Luth[eranorum] practicae.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">His accedit, quod certo d. <persName type="auto_name">Victorinus Strigelius</persName> palam ad nos concessit et in academia <placeName type="auto_name">Lipsensi</placeName> nostram doctrinam et proposuit et defendit.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Authoritas eius multum illis derogabit.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName type="auto_name">Pfeffingerus</persName> se illi opposuit, sed gregarius miles Achilli.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mavult <persName type="auto_name">Victorinus</persName> exilium quam mutare doctrinam.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Contra Tubing[ensis (sc. academia)] vehementer pugnat.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Est haec mutatio dexterae excelsi<note xml:id="fn2" type="footnote" n="2"><cit type="bible"><ref>Ps 77, 11 (Vulg. 76, 11)</ref></cit>.</note> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Datum, Unterschrift und Adresse wurden vom Abschreiber durch einen Vermerk am Briefanfang ersetzt:</hi> Idem eidem. Tiguro Bernam. 9. iunii 1566.</note>]</note>
				</p>
			</div>
